{
 "name": "RPlog_Stranded",
 "title": "Stranded",
 "summary": "Shot down during a fleet engagement, the pilot Raxis -- callsign Spider -- parachutes into the dark, fog-shrouded night side of Dathomir and finds himself tangled in the forest canopy. After climbing down, he is stalked and attacked by a pack of red-eyed, fanged simian predators, fending them off with his Bryar pistol and a flare before escaping across a river. Tracking a distant fire, he discovers another crash site and frees a trapped X-wing pilot, Hotwire of the 234th, from his burning cockpit, dressing the man's wounded leg. The two stranded airmen pool their meager supplies, build a lean-to shelter from the wreckage near some boulders, and debate their best chance of rescue. Confident that ground forces and a recovery team will eventually find them, Raxis takes first watch as they settle in for a long night.",
